    "ecoli_nucleotide_excision_repair",
    "ecoli_mismatch_repair",
    "ecoli_sos_response",
    "ecoli_oxidative_stress_response"
  ],
  "scientificAccuracy": "This flowchart is based on extensive biochemical characterization of E. coli BER enzymes and pathway steps. All molecular components, substrate specificities, and catalytic mechanisms have been validated against primary research. The model represents the current understanding of how bacteria maintain genome integrity through removal and replacement of damaged bases, a pathway conserved across all domains of life.",
